summary: Some tattoos for your Skyrim character
descriptionHtml:
You can find some tattoos I made for my game in this mod, I took the time to put the designs on the textures to make my game more unique.
It includes a body model and the textures that go with it.

NEW in Ver 0.1a
Now 4 new textures to choose from; you need version 0.1 to use this textures, the new file add 4 more options.

Follow the instructions in the README for installation.
